    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Table tops, usually relatively simple, that are placed upon pedestals, saw horses, or other supporting structures to form a table. They may be stored separately from the base, and assembled as needed.</Note_Text>
